  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add garlic and sauté for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add mushrooms and cook until they release their liquid and start to brown.",
    "Add cherry tomatoes, paprika, salt, and pepper. Cook for 3-4 minutes, until the tomatoes start to release their juices.",
    "Add spinach and cook until wilted.",
    "Stir in feta cheese and cook until melted.",
    "Remove from heat and stir in chopped parsley and balsamic vinegar.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
